msgid "Announce Meeting Times and Dates"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/lesson_development/email_templates.md:56
msgid ""
"Subject: First Meeting of the [ carpentry org ] [ lesson title ] Curriculum "
"Advisory Committee"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/lesson_development/email_templates.md:58
#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/lesson_development/email_templates.md:76
msgid "Hi all,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/lesson_development/email_templates.md:60
msgid ""
"Thanks again for being a part of the [lesson title] CAC. We'll be having our"
" first bi-annual meeting to prepare for the [upcoming Bug BBQ or lesson "
"release] which will be held [dates]. To accommodate the geographical "
"diversity of our committee members, we'll be having two meetings. I strongly"
" recommend that those who can attend both do so, as it will help to build "
"consistency across the meetings and a team-feeling for the group. Of course,"
" if you're only able to attend one meeting, that's fine too!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/lesson_development/email_templates.md:62
msgid ""
"The meetings will be at the times linked below (please click the links to "
"see the time in your own time zone). I'll be sending out information about "
"meeting location and agenda early next week."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/lesson_development/email_templates.md:64
msgid ""
"[meeting time 1](link to timeanddate event announcer) [meeting time 2](link "
"to timeanddate event announcer)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/lesson_development/email_templates.md:67
msgid ""
"Please let me know if you have any questions. Looking forward to meeting "
"everyone soon!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/lesson_development/email_templates.md:72
msgid "Follow up from Curriculum Advisory Committee Meeting"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/lesson_development/email_templates.md:74
msgid ""
"Subject: Follow-up Items from [lesson title] Curriculum Advisory Committee "
"Meetings"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/lesson_development/email_templates.md:78
msgid ""
"Thank you again for a very productive set of meetings last week. I've put "
"together minutes for our two meetings (combined in [this document](link to "
"meeting minutes in https://github.com/datacarpentry/curriculum-advisors/)), "
"including decision points and action items for follow-up. I wanted to run "
"these by everyone to make sure that I've correctly identified the decisions "
"that were made before I follow up with the Maintainers to move these "
"decisions forward."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/lesson_development/email_templates.md:80
msgid ""
"It would be greatly appreciated if you could take a look at the minutes and "
"let me know by [date and time UTC](link to timeanddate event announcer) if "
"you see any problems or have any objections to the decisions and action "
"items. At that point, I will follow up with the Maintainers on the next "
"steps."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/lesson_development/email_templates.md:82
msgid ""
"Thank you everyone for bringing your backgrounds and expertise to the "
"meetings last week and for your deep thought about this curriculum. I'm "
"excited about [upcoming publication or major lesson change]."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/lesson_development/email_templates.md:84
msgid "Please let me know if you have any questions or comments."
msgstr ""
